Tolong tunggu disini.

117
00:06:09.257 --> 00:06:10.267
Oke.

118
00:06:15.538 --> 00:06:17.368
Kau sering mengalami sakit kepala akhir-akhir ini.

119
00:06:17.668 --> 00:06:20.108
